<br />
Some other places are:
<br />
- ToV
<br />
- Deep
<br />
- Sleeper (well maybe)
<br />
- and just plane epic hunts to work on coordination.
<br />

<br />
Note: You may have 80 people but if coordination is poor they won't stick around.
